movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: Not as bad as i remembered
review: It was actually very enjoyable and fun to watch. Lightsaber fights were fun and soundtracks were awesome. Yes it does have some cringe but it doesnt bother that much

movie_title: Star Wars: Episode II - Attack of the Clones
title: Not that great
review: Being one of the worst movie of the star wars franchise doesnt mean its bad. Without the cringe romance it would have gotten an 8. It has good action and good cgi for the time.

movie_title: Star Wars: Episode III - Revenge of the Sith
title: One of the best
review: A great movie overall. I really dont understand the hate this movie gets. Soundtrack is spot on like with every other star wars movie. Fight scenes are out of this world. And the dialogue isnt as cringy like with menace or attack of the clones.

movie_title: Star Wars: Episode IV - A New Hope
title: A classic movie
review:
An amazing classic movie everyone knows. Arguably the best sci-fi movie there is.
It changed the face of cinema forever. If you havent seen it you are missing on alot. Truly a masterpiece!!!!
